In an air strike of Israel a senior commander of Hamas has died.
It is the death of 2nd Hamas leader in Israel continual attack for a week in Gaza Strip.
Hamas officials said that Abu Zakaria Aljamal died in Alshujai palace situated in the East of Gaza city on Saturday.
In another Israeli air strike scholar of Hamas Nazaar Rayyan was died on Thursday.
Exile leader of Hamas Khalid Mashal residing in Syria resolved to take revenge and warned Israel for ground attack on Gaza.
Thousand of soldiers and tanks are deployed on Gaza border, they are waiting for orders of launching attack.
